// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1297 — Mass File Rename (ransomhouse)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 180c29ef-b615-57eb-9189-7fc9c87de426

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
